How To Report Crop Insurance Program Fraud and Abuse

   If you suspect fraud, waste, or abuse in the crop insurance program:
     * call USDA's Office of Inspector General (OIG) toll-free hot line at
       1-800-424-9121, Monday-Friday from 8am-4pm EST, or
     * write USDA's Office of Inspector General (OIG), P.O. Box 23399,
       Washington, DC 20026

   When calling or writing, include as much detail as you can. If you
   write and sign your name, let them know if you wish to remain
   confidential.

